headline.main: Embattled French Candidate Fillon to Appear on Sunday Evening News
headline.print_headline: Embattled French Candidate Fillon to Appear on Sunday Evening News

lead_paragraph: French presidential candidate Francois Fillon will speak on France 2 television's Sunday evening news program, the broadcaster said, after he had earlier canceled a Monday morning radio appearance that was to discuss his campaign.
